graph LR
    DSP[Data Science Pipelines Operator]

    %% External Platform Dependencies
    DSP -->|container orchestration| K8s[Kubernetes/OpenShift 4.11+]
    DSP -->|workflow engine v1| Tekton[OpenShift Pipelines<br/>Tekton 1.8+]
    DSP -->|workflow engine v2<br/>bundled, namespace-scoped| Argo[Argo Workflows 3.x]
    DSP -->|metadata storage| DB[MariaDB 10.x+<br/>or External DB]
    DSP -->|artifact storage| S3[S3-compatible Storage<br/>Minio or External]
    DSP -->|external auth| OAuth[OAuth Proxy]
    DSP -->|pod-to-pod TLS| ServiceCA[OpenShift Service CA]

    %% Internal ODH/RHOAI Dependencies
    DSP -.->|UI integration| Dashboard[ODH Dashboard]
    DSP -.->|metrics collection| Monitoring[User Workload Monitoring]
    DSP -.->|metrics aggregation| RHOAIMon[RHOAI Monitoring]
    DSP -.->|pipeline authoring| Workbenches[Workbenches/Notebooks]

    %% Integration Points (who calls DSP)
    Dashboard -->|REST API calls<br/>OAuth| DSP
    Workbenches -->|KFP SDK client<br/>pipeline submission| DSP
    Elyra[Elyra] -->|visual pipeline<br/>authoring/submission| DSP

    %% External Services (egress from DSP components)
    DSP -->|external storage| ExternalS3[External S3<br/>AWS/GCS/Azure]
    DSP -->|external database| ExternalDB[External Database<br/>RDS/CloudSQL]
    DSP -->|container images| Registry[Container Registry]
    DSP -->|pipeline code| Git[Git Repositories]

    %% Kubernetes API Server (central hub)
    DSP -->|CR reconciliation<br/>resource mgmt| K8sAPI[Kubernetes API Server]
    K8s -.->|provides| K8sAPI
    Argo -->|workflow CRs| K8sAPI
    Tekton -->|pipelinerun CRs| K8sAPI

    %% Monitoring relationships
    Monitoring -->|ServiceMonitor scrape| DSP
    RHOAIMon -->|ServiceMonitor scrape| DSP

    %% Certificate provisioning
    ServiceCA -->|auto-provision certs| DSP

    %% Styling
    style DSP fill:#4a90e2,stroke:#333,stroke-width:4px,color:#fff

    %% External platform (gray)
    style K8s fill:#999,stroke:#333,color:#fff
    style Tekton fill:#999,stroke:#333,color:#fff
    style Argo fill:#999,stroke:#333,color:#fff
    style OAuth fill:#999,stroke:#333,color:#fff
    style ServiceCA fill:#999,stroke:#333,color:#fff
    style K8sAPI fill:#999,stroke:#333,color:#fff

    %% Storage (purple)
    style DB fill:#bd10e0,stroke:#333,color:#fff
    style S3 fill:#bd10e0,stroke:#333,color:#fff

    %% Internal ODH (green)
    style Dashboard fill:#7ed321,stroke:#333
    style Monitoring fill:#7ed321,stroke:#333
    style RHOAIMon fill:#7ed321,stroke:#333
    style Workbenches fill:#7ed321,stroke:#333
    style Elyra fill:#7ed321,stroke:#333

    %% External services (orange)
    style ExternalS3 fill:#f5a623,stroke:#333
    style ExternalDB fill:#f5a623,stroke:#333
    style Registry fill:#f5a623,stroke:#333
    style Git fill:#f5a623,stroke:#333
